Note:
Runa Advanced Standard Library: JIT Compiler Core Module

Provides the foundation for just-in-time compilation in Runa, including:
- Bytecode analysis and optimization
- Native code generation for multiple architectures
- Compilation pipeline management
- Code specialization and inlining
- Cross-platform compilation support
- Performance profiling and optimization
- Memory management for generated code
- Integration with Runa's type system

Features:
- Multi-architecture code generation (x86-64, ARM64, RISC-V)
- Advanced bytecode analysis and optimization
- Dynamic compilation with runtime feedback
- Code specialization for hot paths
- Inline caching and method inlining
- Cross-platform compilation support
- Memory-efficient code generation
- Integration with Runa's advanced type system
- AI/agent-friendly compilation optimization
:End Note

Note: JIT Compiler Configuration - Now using centralized configuration system
